<p>
	A beautiful candle in a tin with the sweet aroma of amber and musk. The candle is hand crafted using clary sage and sandalwood essential oils and will burn for approximately 35 hours. It is a bright yellow colour and decorated with lovely white hearts.</p>
<p>
